subject: Soccer
Boycotts
organizations: Real Racing Club de Santander (Soccer Team)
lead_paragraph: Racing Santander players made good on their threat to boycott a Copa del Rey quarterfinal against Real Sociedad over unpaid wages, refusing to play Thursday.
